### ============================================================
### 미션 관리 APIs
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 생성 (PERSONAL)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
### type=PERSONAL 합산 30개 한도 (Mission.MAX_PERSONAL_MISSIONS_PER_USER)
### 한도 초과 시 050104 error.mission.creation_limit_exceeded
### type=GUILD 는 한도 무관
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Morning Exercise",
  "description": "30 minutes of morning exercise every day",
  "type": "PERSONAL",
  "categoryId": 1,
  "visibility": "PUBLIC",
  "missionInterval": "DAILY",
  "durationDays": 30,
  "executionMode": "TIMED",
  "isPinned": false,
  "expPerCompletion": 10,
  "maxParticipants": 10
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 생성 (SIMPLE 모드 - 즉시 완료)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
### SIMPLE 모드: 시간 측정 없이 즉시 완료, 고정 +5 EXP
### 일일 10회까지만 EXP 지급, 초과 시 수행 가능하나 EXP=0
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "물 한 잔 마시기",
  "description": "체크만 하면 끝",
  "type": "PERSONAL",
  "categoryId": 1,
  "visibility": "PRIVATE",
  "missionInterval": "DAILY",
  "executionMode": "SIMPLE",
  "isPinned": true
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 상세 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 내 미션 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/my
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 내 미션 순서 일괄 변경 (QA-71)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/my/reorder
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "ordered_mission_ids": [3, 1, 2]
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 공개 미션 목록 조회 (페이징)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/public?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 길드의 미션 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/guild/1
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 시스템 미션 목록 조회 (미션북)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/system?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 카테고리별 시스템 미션 목록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/system/category/1?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 템플릿으로 미션 추가 (미션북)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/templates/1/add
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 수정
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Morning Exercise",
  "description": "45 minutes of morning exercise",
  "maxParticipants": 20
}

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 공개
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/open
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 시작
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/start
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 완료
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/complete
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 취소
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 삭제
### ----------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

