### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/join
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 참가자 수락 (미션 생성자용)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/participants/1/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 진행 시작
