### 진행률 업데이트
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/progress?progress=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 참가 완료
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/complete-participation
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 탈퇴
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/withdraw
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 참가자 목록
