Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 참가 여부 확인
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/is-participating
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 내 미션 참가 목록
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/my-participations
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ============================================================
### 미션 실행 추적 APIs
### ============================================================

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 수행 시작 (오늘)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/executions/start
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 수행 시작 (특정 날짜)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/executions/2025-01-15/start
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 특정 날짜 실행 완료 처리
### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 응답 필드 (QA-130):
###   - exp_earned: 획득 EXP (SIMPLE 모드 + 일일 한도 도달 시 0)
###   - daily_simple_exp_capped: SIMPLE 일일 EXP 한도(10회) 도달 여부 (true면 EXP=0)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/executions/2025-01-15/complete?note=Completed morning run&shareToFeed=true
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 모든 실행 기록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/executions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 기간별 실행 기록 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/executions/range?startDate=2025-01-01&endDate=2025-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 오늘 실행해야 할 미션 목록
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/executions/today
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 완료율 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/executions/completion-rate
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 수행 취소 (오늘)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/executions/skip
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 미션 수행 취소 (특정 날짜)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/executions/2025-01-15/skip
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 현재 진행 중인 미션 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/executions/in-progress
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 월별 캘린더 데이터 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/executions/monthly?year=2025&month=1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 특정 날짜의 미션 실행 정보 조회
### ----------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/executions/2025-01-15
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 완료된 미션 실행의 노트 업데이트
### ----------------------------------------------------------
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/executions/2025-01-15/note?note=Updated note
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 완료된 미션 실행에 이미지 다중 업로드 (QA-53, 최대 5장)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/executions/2025-01-15/images
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="images"; filename="image-1.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test-image-1.png
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="images"; filename="image-2.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test-image-2.png
--boundary--

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 완료된 미션 실행 이미지 1장 삭제 (URL 기반)
### ----------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/executions/2025-01-15/images?image_url=https://images.level-up-together.com/missions/.../uuid.png
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 완료된 미션 실행을 피드에 공유
### ----------------------------------------------------------
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/executions/2025-01-15/share
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### ----------------------------------------------------------
### 피드 공유 취소
### ----------------------------------------------------------
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/missions/1/executions/2025-01-15/share
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

